Depends: ${misc:Depends}, vitos-base, debsecan, lynis, cron
Description: VITOS CVE hardening + lynis profile + quarterly audit cron
 Ships the VITOS-specific lynis profile, quarterly debsecan/lynis cron
 entries, and the report templates that the security team fills in
 during the SP6 pen-test pass. Reports are written to /var/log/vitos/
 hardening/ and surfaced in the dashboard's Audit page.
